{"prayers":[{"phelps":"BH11209","text":"## Thompson\n\nShort Obligatory Prayer\n\nAs kw'áñsna ta ts'íya wus ha7 szaytn, Olh xa7 lh Kwúkwpi7 lhn skáts'za7, áwi7 ta7s ha7wís tsutsámxw.\n\nA a7 s-hakstsín as tsutána ta ts'íya wus aslhk'emtayp pilaxentsút kn ts7aylh áwi7 ta támas\n\ntá7a han szugwzúgwt, ta ts'íya wus ha skwankwánt ta tákmus ha7 szugwzugwt.\n\n Táwi7 ta7 xwúytsu7h-kwúkwpi7 tlu tsukw ha7wi, ta Sknúxwatip, tatá7a sentsukwmina ta7 wa7áx tlu7 tsukw ha7wi.\n\n \n\nI bear witness, O my God, that Thou has created me to know Thee and to worship Thee. I testify at this moment to my powerlessness and to Thy might, to my poverty and to Thy wealth.\n\nThere is none other God but Thee, the Help in Peril, the Self-subsisting.","name":"Thompson","source":"bahaiprayers.net","version":"f1090772-ed76-44f9-b101-ea2d300006b6","book_cats":{"af":{"cat":"Kort verpligte gebed","order_in_cat":1},"am":{"cat":"አጭሩ (Short)","order_in_cat":1},"ar":{"cat":"الصلاة   الصغيرة","order_in_cat":1},"az":{"cat":"Qısa Namaz","order_in_cat":1},"be":{"cat":"Кароткая абавязковая малітва","order_in_cat":1},"bg":{"cat":"Кратка задължителна молитва","order_in_cat":1},"ca":{"cat":"Oració obligatòria curta","order_in_cat":1},"cs":{"cat":"Krátká denní modlitba","order_in_cat":1},"da":{"cat":"Kort Obligatorisk Bøn","order_in_cat":1},"de":{"cat":"Das kurze Pflichtgebet","order_in_cat":1},"en":{"cat":"Short Obligatory Prayer","order_in_cat":1},"es":{"cat":"Oración obligatoria corta","order_in_cat":1},"fa":{"cat":"نماز صغیر","order_in_cat":1},"fi":{"cat":"Lyhyt velvollisuusrukous","order_in_cat":1},"fr":{"cat":"Prières prescrites","order_in_cat":1},"ha":{"cat":"Sallar Farilla Gajera","order_in_cat":1},"hi":{"cat":"मध्यम अनिवार्य प्रार्थना","order_in_cat":1},"hu":{"cat":"Rövid kötelező ima","order_in_cat":1},"is":{"cat":"Stutta skyldubænin","order_in_cat":1},"it":{"cat":"Preghiera Obbligatoria Breve","order_in_cat":1},"ja":{"cat":"短い必須の祈り","order_in_cat":1},"kl":{"cat":"Pinngitsoorani Qinnutissaq Naatsoq",